classify_emotion        classifies the emotion (e.g. anger, disgust,
                        fear, joy, sadness, surprise) of a set of
                        texts.
classify_polarity       classifies the polarity (e.g. positive or
                        negative) of a set of texts.
create_matrix           creates a document-term matrix.
emotions                a dataset containing words categorized into six
                        emotion categories.
subjectivity            a dataset containing a list of positive and
                        negative subjective words.
